    "Management": {
      "text": "Correct coagulopathy\nOphtho consult (should see ophtho within 24-48 hours)\nTreatment directed at underlying cause\nAvoid\nNSAIDs\nand anticoagulants\nElevate the head of the bed\nTreat\nnausea/vomiting",
